    <note>He Maozhi [26749] He died before he could raise his family and his wife, who was praised in her funerary inscription for her education in the context of a discussion of the role of women, which seems to suggest that Yuan Xie, at least, thought that they should play a role comparable to men outside the family! Maozhi may related to the other Yinxian He, but I keep as an agnaticlly unconnected person for the time being. Yuan Xie, WJ, 21.3b-7b (wife, born Xuan). Not indexed in CBD.</note>
